If you want `null` to become false:

```
fun fromJson(value: Int?): Boolean {
      return 
}
```

If you want `null` to stay `null` (you&#39;ll also have to modify the `toJson` fun to accept nulls as well then):

```
fun fromJson(value: Int?): Boolean? {
	return value?.let { it == 1 }
}
```

